Author: Mark Fink
Author-email: mark@mark-fink.de
License: MIT
Description: |License| |GitHub issues|
        
        installation
        ============
        
        to install:
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            $ pip install metrics.gitinfo
        
        to uninstall:
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            $ pip uninstall metrics.gitinfo
        
        for details please see the documentation of metrics.
        
        metrics.gitinfo
        ===============
        
        The **metrics.gitinfo** package is a plugin for the existing metrics
        package.
        
        Acknowledgements
        ================
        
        -  much of my work has been inspired by `Adam Tornhills new
           book <http://www.mark-fink.de/2018-04-28-software-design-x-rays/>`__
        -  for reading the git repo we use GitPython
           (https://github.com/gitpython-developers/GitPython)
        -  to find file changes in the repo we use
           https://github.com/Bachmann1234/diff-cover
        
